<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/LISALandCoverClassValue/1_2_4_Screes> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Screes come to be through physical disintegration of geological formations and are the result of becoming smaller and smaller along time. They are accumulated on site due to sedimentary processes or human activity. Further subdivision is made according to their particle size and constellation."@en <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/LISALandCoverClassValue:1> .
