<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/LISALandCoverClassValue/1_Abiotic> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Any unvegetated surfaces, either covered with man-made artificial structures or geologically natural material surfaces (with or without anthropogenic influence or impact)."@en <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/LISALandCoverClassValue:1> .
