<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/LISALandCoverClassValue/1_3_Water> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Wasser"@de <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/LISALandCoverClassValue:1> .
<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/LISALandCoverClassValue/1_3_7_SnowIce> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "snow/ice"@en <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/LISALandCoverClassValue:1> .
